<span id="freeTextContainer15363248354353611219">This is one of the best books I have read all year. I responded to each of the characters from the depths of my heart. Eldonna is a masterful storyteller. I loved this I know, but this one is only better. My friends know I rarely give 5 stars to a book, but I would give 10 to this one if I could. Clover, Harmony, Rain are all etched in my heart.<br/>I listened to it on Audible and heard it almost non stop. I could not stop reading!!!<br/>I have book club today and am going to select it for our July book.<br/></span>

